data.description: Centrally located near Nike & Intel, close to max and Tanasbourne. This spacious home features 4 bds, tech nook, large great room with granite slab counters & stainless steel appliances. Enjoy the captivating view of hall creek and surrounding trees from large back deck, master bedroom & luxurious master bath. HOA maintains landscaping, walking trails surrounding neighborhood & community park. Appliances included. Under bldr warranty.
data.whatILove: The views! The Creek is so pretty all year round and it's great not having to look into anyone else's backyard or at their house. The open floor plan is great for entertaining and having large groups over. The placement of the home in the neighborhood allows for playing in the front yard and is a short walk to the community park. Easily walk to the max stop for down town commuting, and minutes from Streets of Tanasbourne.  Upgrades throughout the home with full granite slab counters and island, upgraded stainless steel appliances, engineered hardwood throughout main, 8 lb carpet, custom storage in the garage. An all around great location and home.
